---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Building the Foundational Model for the Human Body
description: Samaritan is building AI-powered biomarker intelligence, starting with the world's most accessible biofluid. AroBag is our first product — a smart urine monitoring system for ICU patients.
---

{# JSON-LD Structured Data #}
{% block head %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Organization",
  "name": "Samaritan AI",
  "legalName": "{{ site.companyName }}",
  "url": "{{ site.url }}",
  "logo": "{{ site.url }}/assets/samaritan-wide-wordmark.png",
  "foundingDate": "2019-09-12",
  "description": "{{ site.description }}",
  "address": {
    "@type": "PostalAddress",
    "addressLocality": "Bengaluru",
    "addressRegion": "Karnataka",
    "addressCountry": "IN"
  },
  "founder": [
    { "@type": "Person", "name": "Karan Rao" },
    { "@type": "Person", "name": "Raghav Gopal Behl" }
  ]
}
</script>

<noscript>
  <style>
    .reveal { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .mobile-nav-overlay, .mobile-nav-drawer { display: none !important; }
  </style>
</noscript>
{% endblock %}

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="deck-section landing-hero">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <p class="eyebrow reveal">Advanced Urine Parameter Monitoring</p>
    <h1 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Automated Urine Collection &amp; Analysis</h1>
    <p class="hero-lead reveal reveal-delay-2">
      Continuous monitoring of urine output, color, turbidity, and hematuria
      for catheterized patients. Providing healthcare providers with timely
      data to support their clinical assessment and patient care.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-ctas reveal reveal-delay-3">
      <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}?subject=Demo%20Request" class="btn-primary">
        <i class="ph-fill ph-calendar-blank" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        Request Demo
      </a>
      <a href="/arobag/" class="btn-outline">
        Learn More
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <img src="/assets/hero-gradient.svg" alt="" class="hero-gradient" aria-hidden="true">
</section>

