</section>

<!-- What AroBag Measures -->
<section class="deck-section measures-section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow eyebrow-accent">What AroBag Measures — Continuously</p>
    <h2 class="text-center reveal">Multi-parameter sensing that transforms routine monitoring into actionable clinical intelligence.</h2>
    <div class="measures-grid">
      <div class="card card-glass card-sm card-hoverable measures-card reveal">
        <div class="measures-icon"><i class="ph-fill ph-drop" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        <h4>Volume &amp; Flow Monitoring</h4>
        <p>Precise measurement of urine output volume and flow rate to assist clinicians with monitoring for oliguria and anuria.<sup>[1]</sup></p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-glass card-sm card-hoverable measures-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="measures-icon"><i class="ph-fill ph-palette" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        <h4>Urine Color Analysis</h4>
        <p>Spectrophotometric analysis of urine color to provide data that may help identify hydration status and other potential conditions.<sup>[2]</sup></p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-glass card-sm card-hoverable measures-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="measures-icon"><i class="ph-fill ph-eye" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        <h4>Turbidity Measurement</h4>
        <p>Optical analysis of urine clarity to provide data on cloudiness levels that may correlate with crystalluria, infection, or other conditions.<sup>[3]</sup></p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-glass card-sm card-hoverable measures-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="measures-icon"><i class="ph-fill ph-heartbeat" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        <h4>Hematuria Assessment</h4>
        <p>Detection of red blood cell presence in urine through advanced optical sensing to support clinical decision-making.<sup>[4]</sup></p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-glass card-sm card-hoverable measures-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="measures-icon"><i class="ph-fill ph-chart-line-up" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        <h4>Real-Time Monitoring</h4>
        <p>Continuous data collection and trend analysis for timely notification of clinically significant changes in urine parameters.<sup>[5]</sup></p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-glass card-sm card-hoverable measures-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="measures-icon"><i class="ph-fill ph-graph" aria-hidden="true"></i></div>
        <h4>Analytical Support</h4>
        <p>Data analysis tools that can help healthcare providers identify potential patterns requiring clinical attention.<sup>[6]</sup></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Clinical Evidence Section -->
<section class="deck-section-short clinical-evidence-section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow eyebrow-accent">Clinical Evidence</p>
    <h2 class="text-center reveal">Clinical &amp; Economic Impact</h2>
    <p class="section-description reveal reveal-delay-1">
      The cost of missed or delayed detection compounds across patient outcomes and healthcare systems.
    </p>
    <div class="clinical-stats-grid">
      <div class="card card-light card-md stat-card reveal">
        <div class="stat-number">68%</div>
        <p class="stat-label">AKI cases went undetected in hospitalized patients in a clinical cohort study.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-light card-md stat-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="stat-number">2M</div>
        <p class="stat-label">Estimated global AKI-related deaths per year, highlighting the scale of critical-care deterioration.</p>
        <p class="stat-source"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23744003" target="_blank" rel="noopener">deaths/yr — PubMed</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-light card-md stat-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="stat-number">+3.5</div>
        <p class="stat-label">Day increase in average hospital length of stay associated with AKI.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-light card-md stat-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="stat-number">39%</div>
        <p class="stat-label">Urine output data is missed in studies.</p>
        <p class="stat-source">
          <a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-021-97026-8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nature</a> ·
          <a href="https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(11)61454-2/abstract" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Lancet</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="deck-section cta-section" id="contact">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <p class="eyebrow eyebrow-accent reveal">Get in Touch</p>
    <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Let's talk about the future of kidney care</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
      Whether you're an investor, hospital administrator, or clinician — we'd love to show you what Samaritan is building.
    </p>
    <div class="cta-buttons reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}?subject=Meeting%20Request" class="btn-white">
        <i class="ph-fill ph-calendar-blank" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        Book a Meeting
      </a>
      <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}?subject=General%20Inquiry" class="btn-outline-white">
        <i class="ph-fill ph-envelope-simple" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        Send Us a Message
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="cta-hiring reveal reveal-delay-3">
      We're hiring in Bengaluru — <a href="/about/#open-positions">see open positions</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
